==商业表现==
《你让我》在[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]上首次上榜并排名第五，比其歌曲《[[Wake_Me_Up_(艾维奇歌曲)|Wake Me Up]]》在当周高出一位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/jason-derulo-scores-second-week-at-number-1-with-talk-dirty-2517/ |title=Jason Derulo scores second week at Number 1 with Talk Dirty |publisher=Officialcharts.com |date=2013-09-29 |accessdate=2014-01-09 |archive-date=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207211734/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/jason-derulo-scores-second-week-at-number-1-with-talk-dirty-2517/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歌曲还在{{le|英国舞曲排行榜|UK Dance Singles and Albums Charts}}上首次上榜便击败了《Wake Me Up》，排名榜单第一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/jason-derulo-knocks-katy-perry-off-the-top-of-the-official-singles-chart-2502/ |title=Jason Derulo knocks Katy Perry off the top of the Official Singles Chart |publisher=Officialcharts.com |date=2013-09-22 |accessdate=2014-01-09 |archive-date=2014-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709111508/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/jason-derulo-knocks-katy-perry-off-the-top-of-the-official-singles-chart-2502/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在美国，《你让我》在2013年10月5日首次登上[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]第85位，但只上榜了一周时间<ref name=BB85 />。

==在流行文化中==
《你让我》被用于[[ITV2|ITV2]]《Freshers》的广告宣传，这是一部关于[[贝德福德大学|贝德福德大学]]{{le|新生周|Student orientation}}的电视纪录片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lutontoday.co.uk/what-s-on/arts-culture/students-star-in-tv-freshers-show-1-5592004|title=Students star in TV Freshers show|work=Luton Today|accessdate=2020-07-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092659/http://www.lutontoday.co.uk/what-s-on/arts-culture/students-star-in-tv-freshers-show-1-5592004|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲也被{{le|十大体育网|Sony Ten}}用于2013 - 14年印度和南非进行的[[板球|板球]]系列赛<ref>{{YouTube|PBBEDjls4j0|India's Tour of South Africa 2013 Live on TEN CRICKET by jagman}}</ref>。

2014年4月，《你让我》被用作[[Spotify|Spotify]]商业广告《Can't Find the Words?》的背景音乐<ref>{{cite web|title=Can't Find The Words?|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YnNhFVf2ULo|publisher=Youtube|accessdate=2014-04-28|author=Spotify|date=2014-04-10|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121033949/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YnNhFVf2ULo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

